Class LeasedBindable<T>

Namespace
osu.Framework.Bindables
Assembly
osu.Framework.dll

A bindable carrying a mutually exclusive lease on another bindable. Can only be retrieved via BeginLease(bool).

public class LeasedBindable<T> : Bindable<T>, IParseable, ILeasedBindable<T>, ILeasedBindable, IBindable, IBindable<T>, ICanBeDisabled, IHasDefaultValue, IUnbindable, IHasDescription, IFormattable
